FIG. 8 Habitus of 
<taxonomicName authority="Tian &amp; Chen &amp; Ma, 2020" authorityName="Tian &amp; Chen &amp; Ma" authorityYear="2020" box="[336,536,1946,1970]" class="Insecta" family="Carabidae" genus="Miaotrechus" kingdom="Animalia" order="Coleoptera" pageId="8" pageNumber="583" phylum="Arthropoda" rank="species" species="heweii" status="n. sp.">
